title: Synology NAS: RAID Status
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/storagehw/synology
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the health and current Status of
 Raids configured on a Synology NAS device.
 The check returns an {CRIT} in case of an error state reported
 by the device (Degrade, Crashed) and {WARN} at all other RAID operations (but for OK, Raid Syncing and Raid Parity Checking)

item:
 The name of the Raid Volume like reported in the MIB

inventory:
 One check is created for Volume

